  "description": "Shadow archetype. Subharmonic-heavy, detuned clusters, odd partials emphasized. Dark throat formant pitched down an octave. High effort with low sync creates a guttural, almost terrifying voice singing from the underworld. O-to-Alien vowel ensures nothing sounds human.",
